ds/2025/04/NintendoSwitch2-HW-11-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/nintendo-switch-2">Nintendo Switch 2</a>的预订今天早些时候（4月4日）在许多英国零售商处上线 - 他们已经售罄。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/guides/gaming-guides/nintendo-switch-2-launch-games-3851363">每个已确认的Nintendo Switch 2启动游戏</a></li></ul><p>Switch 2于今年早些时候首次在 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/nintendo-switch-2-release-date-price-games-3829607">以硬件为中心的预告片中</a>宣布，任天堂<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/nintendo-switch-2-release-date-price-pre-order-3851248">在本周的直接演示中</a>透露了有关该控制台的更多信息。</p><p> Nintendo Switch 2将于6月5日发布，价格为395.99英镑。为了阻止脱烫手掌握控制台并以高昂的价格转售它， <a href="https://store.nintendo.co.uk/en/nintendo-switch-2?srsltid=AfmBOordt62Sj4zn9qzS3slywFJaxRipzJEmc-e7gR75FkgZULO7yOtd" target="_blank" rel="noopener">任天堂官方商店</a>将优先考虑那些在原始开关上超过50个小时的玩家，并在下周（4月8日）上线时拥有活跃的Nintendo会员资格。</p><p>然而，许多英国零售商将其Nintendo Switch 2预订现场直播，许多零售商已经出售了。玩具公司<a href="https://www.smythstoys.com/uk/en-gb/gaming-and-tech/nintendo-switch-2/nintendo-switch-2-consoles/nintendo-switch-2-mario-kart-world-pack/p/249606" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Smyths</a> ，购物网站<a href="https://www.very.co.uk/promo/nintendo-switch-launch">非常非常好</a>，而<a href="https://www.argos.co.uk/vp/oos/SoldOut_Version_HoldingPage_uk_pdp.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Argos</a>目前正在各自的网站上显示出库存消息，而<a href="https://www.currys.co.uk/brand/nintendo/nintendo-announcement.html">库里（Currys）</a>暂时仅在商店中进行预订。</p><p>亚马逊还托管了仅邀请的预订系统，从彩票中选择的22小时以购买开关2的彩票。您可以<a href="https://www.amazon.co.uk/nintendo-switch-2/s?k=nintendo+switch+2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>申请。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Nintendo Switch 2  - 概述预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9flte56erE8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/nintendo-switch-2-price-backlash-preorder-3851527">许多粉丝对Switch 2的“疯狂”成本感到愤怒</a>之后。尽管控制台的价格为395.99英镑，但<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/mario-kart-9">Mario Kart World</a></em>的实物副本将使您返回74.99英镑，而新的3D Platformer <em>Donkey Kong Bananza的</em>价格为66.99英镑，而该游戏的数字版本则为58.99英镑。玩家还必须付费才能升级当前的交换机游戏，以利用特殊的Switch 2更新。</p><p>一位粉丝在社交媒体上<a href="https://x.com/SendoDX/status/1907454691144806885" target="_blank" rel="noopener">写道</a>：“我真的认为Switch 2将成为任天堂的代际幻想。这些价格标签围绕其发行造成了否定性，我实际上感到震惊。他们操了这个坏处。”</p><p>昨晚在正式的直播中，心怀不满的玩家向随附的聊天垃圾邮件，并鼓励任天堂“<a href="https://x.com/CultureCrave/status/1907966169749008572" target="_blank" rel="noopener">降低价格</a>”。今年早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/switch-2-affordable-nintendo-price-details-cost-3835946">任天堂老板承诺新台可以负担得起。</a></p><p>这是在关于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/gta6-could-cost-100-says-industry-expert-but-player-backlash-would-be-significant-3832530">摇滚明星游戏的谣言，希望</a>为侠盗猎车手<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/grand-theft-auto-vi">6（Grand Theft Auto 6）</a></em>收取100美元（76英镑）的收费。</p><p>在其他新闻中， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/bloodborne">Bloodborne的</a></em>粉丝对<em>Duskbloods的</em><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/nintendo-switch-2">Switch 2</a>游戏感到非常兴奋， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/bloodborne-2-the-duskbloods-switch-2-fromsoftware-3851572">许多人认为这是动作幻想冠军的精神继任者</a>。</p><p>邮政<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/nintendo-switch-2-pre-orders-uk-amazon-argos-game-3851930">开关2预订已经售罄，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Zakk Wylde回想起与Ozzy Osbourne巡回演出中最“健康”的时刻：“我们就像几个顽皮的学校孩子们” https://www.nme.com/news/music/zakk-wylde-recalls-most-most-wholome-moment-on-tour-on-tour-with-ozzy-ozzy-osbourne-3851915?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = zakk-wylde-recalls-recalls-wholome-wollome-momment-on-tour-tour-with-oszzy-osbourneLiberty Dunworth Fri, 04 Apr 2025 10:30:49 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetal https://www.nme.com/?p=3851915 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Ozzy Osbourne和Zakk Wylde" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>事件发生在他们两个在日本巡回演出时发生</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/zakk-wylde-recalls-most-wholesome-moment-on-tour-with-ozzy-osbourne-3851915">Zakk Wylde帖子回想起与Ozzy Osbourne一起巡回演出的最“健康”的时刻：“我们就像几个顽皮的孩子们一样”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Ozzy Osbourne和Zakk Wylde" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zakk-wylde">Zakk Wylde</a>回忆起与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ozzy-osbourne">Ozzy Osbourne一起在新采访中与Ozzy Osbourne</a>巡回演出的最“健康”时刻。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/ozzy-osbourne-tour-retirement-black-sabbath-3390656"><b>Ozzy Osbourne：摇滚乐表演者与众不同</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>这位吉他手已经与Metal Pioneer和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">Black Sabbath</a>主持人合作了几十年，并加入了他的独奏材料，并一起进行了无数的旅行。现在，在对<em><a href="https://www.loudersound.com/metal-hammer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Metal Hammer</a></em>的新采访中，Wylde回顾了他从旅途中开始的一些最好的轶事。</p><p>在讨论期间，Wylde被要求与奥斯本（Osbourne）分享他认为最“有益健康的”的时间，他解释了这两个时刻，他们两个人偷偷一起偷偷一起在浴室里喝啤酒。</p><p> “我记得我们在东京扮演了布坎[竞技场]。我总是随身携带一袋啤酒，以防万一我们要去任何啤酒的地方，” <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-label-society">Black Label Society</a>成员开始说道。</p><p> “所以，演出后，绿野仙子进了房间。我走了，“是的，我不会在这里给你开除的！ </p><figure id="attachment_3851922" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3851922" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3851922" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde-1989@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Ozzy Osbourne和Zakk Wylde，1989年" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde-1989@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde-1989@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde-1989@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde-1989@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde-1989@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ozzy-wylde-1989@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3851922" class="wp-caption-text"> Ozzy Osbourne和Zakk Wylde于1989年。信贷：Paul Natkin/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “ [Ozzy]去，&#39;好吧，告诉你，我会在浴室里见你。&#39;所以我在浴室里等着。他将其倒下，将罐头放下，然后将其推回去，“谢谢，我在晚餐时见。”</p><p>他补充说：“我们就像几个顽皮的小学生！这很有趣！”</p><p>评论发表在Wylde今年早些时候与<em>EMGTV</em>进行了另一次采访之后，并透露，他在录音室中最“令人难忘的”时刻是当他听到他与Ozzy Osbourne在广播电台上演的工作时。</p><p> “Actually hearing the playback and when it was done, and then I remember the first time I heard it on the radio,” he said, referring to the song &#39;Miracle Man&#39; (via <em><a href="https://blabbermouth.net/news/zakk-wylde-names-his-most-memorable-recording-studio-moment" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Blabbermouth</a></em> ).</p><p> “That was pretty monumental. It was the first song I ever wrote with the boss, and then the first song with the boss I ever heard on the radio. So, yeah, that was pretty monumental.”</p><p> Wylde&#39;s comments about Ozzy come as the legendary frontman is set to reunite with his Black Sabbath bandmates this summer and <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-sabbath-final-show-birmingham-july-2025-metalla-slayer-pantera-line-up-tickets-3835042">play one final live concert at Villa Park in their Birmingham hometown</a> on Saturday July 5. </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DFu3ZyBzEea/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></di